        { "id": "grammar-01", "type": "text", "content": "**Prepositions of place:**\n- *next to, opposite, between, near, far from*\n\n**Imperatives for directions:**\n- *Go straight, turn left, turn right, take the first/second street*\n\n**Modal 'can' for requests:**\n- *Can you tell me where…?*" }
